{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"39945-where-is-my-friend","title":"Yuko Wapi Rafiki Yangu?","description":"Nia anamtafuta rafiki yake. Kila mara rafiki yake anafanikiwa kujificha na kumpa Nia wakati mgumu kumtafuta. Alimpaka rangi tofautitofauti ili aweze kumuona kwa urahisi, lakini bado alifanikiwa kujificha. Mwishowe Nia aligundua mbimu za kujificha rafiki yake. Je, Nia aligundua nini?","language":"Kiswahili","langCode":"sw","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Tebogo Maganye"],"illustrators":["Michael  Sagikwa"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/39945-where-is-my-friend"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101397/size3/14639f531b6a18cf75cdd0320a178dca.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101397/size6/14639f531b6a18cf75cdd0320a178dca.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76910/size6/afaaeabc17fa514704e5cd5015d5f606.jpg","text":"Nia hamuoni rafiki yake. Kila wakati huwa anajificha. Nia anapata taabu kumtafuta. Nia anawaza… Oh! Nia amepata suluhisho.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76911/size6/87763cc91bd176420289a34384124cc9.jpg","text":"Siku ya Jumatatu, alimpaka rangi nyekundu. Ili amuone kwa urahisi. “Uko wapi?” Nia anamtafuta.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76912/size6/d47a0bbd54f75ff891541ae7b713306b.jpg","text":"“Niko kwenye matufaa mekundu.”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76913/size6/3dc2e8236f02547aaa45519fb7a277e1.jpg","text":"Siku ya Jumanne alimpaka rangi ya chungwa ili amuone kwa urahisi.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76914/size6/d3782eec1e7bc57f6759284c02df4f80.jpg","text":"Rafiki yake akajificha kwenye matunda.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76915/size6/f875a1b8a8d3cd03f7d00b8642abbbad.jpg","text":"Siku ya Jumatano nayo alimpaka \nrangi ya manjano. \"Nikimpaka \nrangi hii nitamuona kwa urahisi.\" Nia aliwaza.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76916/size6/309f161d293c94d926908d01371c2c69.jpg","text":"Tazama niko huku.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76917/size6/097699ffee24f9cdcc3aa6f9dbbb5f16.jpg","text":"Siku ya Alhamisi, aliamua kumpaka \nrangi ya kijani.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76918/size6/6c6d818e0b3ba4d2fc28eed47f3c1739.jpg","text":"Tazama rafiki yake Nia alikojificha.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76919/size6/a67bb2f6ce92dd1e5d3dbe8697d669bf.jpg","text":"Siku ya Ijumaa, alimpaka rangi ya samawati.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76920/size6/2c66713eb239e5ea6f80752b5af6e6e8.jpg","text":"Rafiki alijificha kwenye picha iliyobandikwa ukutani.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76921/size6/c80db32a6fa8a3d135d4dd41552ce175.jpg","text":"Siku ya Jumamosi alimpaka yangi ya zambarau.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76922/size6/220654274e132c65ee6012ca570a1d73.jpg","text":"Alijificha kwenye zabibu mbivu.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76923/size6/fa242cd37861b004b0707a178eba4a8e.jpg","text":"Siku ya Jumapili, Nia alipata suluhisho. Alimpaka rangi za upinde wa mvua.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/76924/size6/af13d1260cdca322d4e590677ee2a870.jpg","text":"Oh! Leo rafiki yake Nia hana tena pa kujificha. Anaonekana kwa urahisi.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":132}}